- Fixed bottom-right
- Bronze circular button with up arrow
- Smooth scroll to top
- Fade in/out animation

Task 3: Breadcrumb System (if multi-page)

If adding more pages:
- Breadcrumb navigation
- Shows current location
- Links back to home/portfolio

Task 4: Loading States

Add loading UI:
- Skeleton screens for portfolio
- Loading spinner for form submission
- Image loading placeholders
- Smooth content reveals

